{"tid":572894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打介唔介意養自己條女?","createTime":"2018-02-26T03:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T04:30:03.000Z","uid":146998,"like":25,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6daf95f8b8c03e3a426785d1c7aa39397e48dee7","tid":572894,"uid":146998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"我係學生<br />\n老豆老母從來唔比零用錢<br />\n最多1個月比幾百蚊我入8達通<br />\n所以我極慳<br />\n雖然有番pt<br />\n但都極少成日出街洗錢/ social <br />\n因為平時番學已經要洗自己錢食飯 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔介意出街散下步做下運動<br />\n做啲唔洗消費既野<br />\n但事實係食飯都要錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男朋友又要成日見 <br />\n佢又想我陪佢睇戲<br />\n所以我地都勁少aa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮 : 唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮 : 分手啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  累人累物"},{"pid":"b475e4e638279ee99dc6ccf96b0830614f5467ef","tid":572894,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:49:36.000Z","msg":"我養你"},{"pid":"d8f4c663e3c71aea136af4c034dafe2b52f58b23","tid":572894,"uid":108236,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"屌閪唔洗錢咩依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579e97358dae8139ae9305d049e668a07608a909","tid":572894,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"佢係咪做緊野先<br />\n如果係 佢又唔介意 咁你介意d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ca9ebcd5a543e1686cd7e9bad8e1b8748eb5c3","tid":572894,"uid":100131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"你可以直接同佢講, 其實男仔好多時都唔知女仔想點, 佢叫你去睇戲, 你肯去, 佢咪以為你鐘意睇戲囉<br />\n<br />\n講多少少, 可以促進發展, 靠估好辛苦"},{"pid":"96f06f7dde15759fb72a62a6d71e199cb3d8b340","tid":572894,"uid":139709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea178e2d5fa5744f0f795c0bf027824fe9772b81","tid":572894,"uid":55847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"真係愛你  知你無咩收入  又點會唔比埋<br />\n不過前提係你值唔值人地愛/對方係咪PLAYER"},{"pid":"9dfe070a25c8e16ac87cb04442eaccf108754e5a","tid":572894,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"因住雞包仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042b329a43158744717c3f031248e4fd9e52d588","tid":572894,"uid":128964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"睇下條仔有冇錢咯<br />\n個人意見：如果我未出黎打工用老豆老母錢嘅 我就應該aa啊 相反 如果我出左黎打工 我覺得花錢起女女身上係應該嘅<br />\n反正就係睇條仔成唔成熟啦 如果我係條仔知道你咁慘嘅 我ot都會養你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf17b2cab828d91c492ff0106531f5161cae85cd","tid":572894,"uid":72186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"花錢養人哋老婆就唔抵<br />\n養自己條女無所謂啦"},{"pid":"c7b228da7e454d4575a0e0163eb896a3367d70eb","tid":572894,"uid":149323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"你比佢屌 佢養你 公平交易"},{"pid":"c8fff388c68b70742ef59b3b10871378d5c7c879","tid":572894,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"你都要睇下男朋友有無錢<br />\n<br />\n番緊學既養自己都窄窄地，點養多條女?"},{"pid":"631087903c94eefcfbacda3462f9a0e8e2f0d596","tid":572894,"uid":145923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T04: